sourceMeaningMnemonic: The <radical>leader</radical> <radical>cat pirate</radical> is the greatest cat pirate of them all. It leads all the cat pirate leaders, even! This is truly a cat pirate <kanji>to look up to</kanji>.
meaningInfo: Imagine this majestic cat pirate leader of leaders. Feel in your heart that you look up to this cat pirate, truly.
readingMnemonic: Your job is to bring this leader of cat pirates (whom you <kanji>look up to</kanji>) its favorite food: <reading>gyo</reading>za (<ja>ぎょう</ja>).
readingInfo: Of course, the gyoza is filled with fish, because we're talking about cat pirates, here.
